Time to get back on the zero based budget again to get us back on track.

And yes these are our actual income and expense amounts for this week. (I totally don't give a sh*t if people know our income, it's just a number)

Today is payday so I've transferred the mortgage money into our bill sinking fund account for when it's due in 2 weeks.

I've purchased our e gift card for groceries through our NRMA membership and I've loaded up my opal card for the next week.

All the other transfers and bpay payments are scheduled for Thursday and I'll mark off the other expenses as we use up the funds. 
The right hand column shows the things that need to come out of our other bank/income and the coin jar 🙊.
